Summary: Unit Testing Framework for C/C++
Name: cutter
Version: 1.2.7
Release: 2%{?dist}
License: LGPLv3+
URL: http://cutter.sourceforge.net/
Source: http://downloads.sourceforge.net/cutter/cutter-%{version}.tar.gz
BuildRequires:  gcc-c++
